{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"008d082e56","title":"关于迁回部队突击京汉、龙海线等问题致张学良电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b4f1663174","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"008d082e56"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"be931ef71f","type":"paragraph","text":"关于迁回部队突击京汉、龙海线等问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"1e945872b6","type":"paragraph","text":"致张学良电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"8c4042b182","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月17日）李毅兄","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"6bf9c45109","type":"paragraph","text":"签电奉悉，集力抗战甚妥。惟对敌意见，弟认胡宗南、汤恩伯均不过一支队，各以一部钳制之可也，敌之要害在南京与京汉、陇海线，若以二三万人之战略迁回部队突击京汉、陇海取得决定胜利，则大局立起变化，此点祈考虑。我们对远方叫已作几个报告，尚无回报。兄令刘鼎将每日群众运动情形电告一次，若远方知此次事变及事变后之进展不是单纯军事行动，而是与民众联系的，估计当寄以同情。惟远方政府目前为应付外交，或尚不能公开赞助我们。恩来在肤施城外等候，请速伤肤施民团让出该城。如何盼复","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"d0bff5f62f","type":"paragraph","text":"弟赵东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"f987ea7b40","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日[1]指共产国际。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"},{"id":"3f91673f5d","type":"paragraph","text":"应张学良邀请，中共中央派周恩来、叶剑英、博古（秦邦宪）到西安参加谈判。1936年12月17日，周恩来一行飞抵西安，立即和张学良举行会谈。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56"}],"page":{"id":"10277dc0e3","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"008d082e56","start":178,"end":179}}}},"__N_SSG":true}